research/history/round_summaries/round_0131.json:7:  "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0131.json:19:    "hypothesis": "最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x) u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，e(·) 是轻量 router 选择的单个静态 expert。在线侧可导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_topk` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r130 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 切到 `lowrank_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r130 在约 0.29x total_cost 下的失败是否主要来自“always-on shared low-rank branch + single routed expert”这一异构组合本身；如果 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在近同成本下明显优于 r130 的 FVU=0.2266，则说明当前低成本瓶颈更偏向 shared+routed 结构耦合，而不是单-expert lowrank+expert 这条线整体失效。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0131.json:20:    "summary": "Round 131 不继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做第三个非支配失败后的局部 probe，而是做一次 matched-cost 结构切换。建议以 r130 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk`，在近同样的 <0.3x 总成本下直接比较“shared low-rank + routed expert”与“low-rank trunk + single expert”谁更值得继续。",
research/history/round_summaries/round_0131.json:23:    "family_name": "lowrank_expert_topk",
