research/history/logs/agent_round_0192.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"lower_fvu","experiment_tier":"proxy","family_name":"shared_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family 设为 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。最终重构公式为 `x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(r)} Σ_{j∈S_e(r)} γ_{e,j}(r) c_{e,j}`，其中 `r = x - Σ_{i∈S_sh(x)} α_i^sh(x) u_i`，`{u_i}` 是 shared coarse 静态向量库，`{c_{e,j}}` 是 expert residual 静态子库。在线侧可直接导出为 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 查表+加权求和，再对 residual 做 expert 子库选择、查表与选择性补偿”流水线，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`。唯一主假设：相对 r190 仅切换到 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`，在保持 `K=96`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 的 very-short-path low-cost recipe 下，显式把 cheap shared/coarse branch 与 expert residual cleanup 分工开来，会比当前 r190 的 `lowrank_expert_topk` 更有效地稳住 small-K 质量，并在约 `0.20x total_cost` 内把 FVU 明显压低。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果这轮在约 0.20x 下显著优于 r190，下一轮优先继续留在该 family，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO` 来校准 shared coarse 与 residual cleanup 的预算分配。","如果这轮仍明显弱于 `<0.25x` anchors，则可基本结束这条 trunk-free shared-coarse+expert-cleanup 低成本槽位，把预算转回别的 architecture-level probe。"],"notes_to_memory":["本地成本自检：在 r190 exact recipe 上切到 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 后，selection≈0.11x、deployment≈0.09x、combined≈0.20x，处于 `<0.25x` 主战场且低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮不是继续沿 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 或 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做 K/LATENTS 插值，而是用当前最新可用 reference r190 做一次 matched-cost architecture swap，直接回答 small-K 下“cheap shared main branch + expert cleanup”是否比单 trunk+expert 更稳。"],"reference_round":190,"self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r190 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。没有新增 tunable 参数，也没有代码改动，因此不需要触碰 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。选择它而不是再试 `factorized_expert_topk`/`shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk`，是因为当前策略更强调“先用 cheap shared/coarse branch 吃掉平滑主干，再让 experts 做 sparse residual cleanup”，而 `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` 正好在 `<0.25x` 内最直接回答这个问题。主要风险是该 family 先前在更高 K 配方下已接近但未打赢当前 low-cost anchor；但本轮用更小 K、当前最新 reference 的 fresh matched probe，信息增量仍然高。","summary":"建议以 r190 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次落在 `<0.25x` 主战场内的 matched architecture probe，用当前 `K=96` 小支撑配方直接检验“shared coarse branch + expert residual cleanup”是否能比现有 low-cost 非主线探针更慢地退化。","touched_files":[]}
