research/history/logs/agent_round_0157.stdout.log:511:shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual {"status": "active", "design_hypothesis": "最终重构公式：x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 为 shared 静态向量库，{B_e} 为 routed expert 静态子库，C={c_m} 为全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared 查表 + routed 子库查表 + 选择性 residual 补偿 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容。唯一主假设：相对 r146 只把 ARCHITECTURE 从 lowrank_expert_residual 切到 shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual，保持 K=112、EF=1、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、NUM_EXPERTS=64、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 与其余训练配方不变，做一次 matched-cost 结构对照，直接回答“shared low-rank basis + routed expert + residual”在约 0.55x total_cost 下是否比当前 trunk-based lowrank_expert_residual 更值得继续。", "tested_configs": [{"round": 138, "stage": "prototype", "k": "128", "decision": "keep", "val_fvu": "0.09455648809671402", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 139, "stage": "stabilize", "k": "128", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.1511169672012329", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 140, "stage": "stabilize", "k": "128", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.10045520961284637", "run_health": "normal"}, {"round": 147, "stage": "stabilize", "k": "112", "decision": "discard", "val_fvu": "0.10375456511974335", "run_health": "normal"}], "known_issues": [], "next_steps": ["若该点在约 0.55x 成本下接近或优于 r146 的 FVU，则下一轮只改 K 或 STAGE1_RATIO，把这条 hetero-MoE+residual 线向 0.5x 左侧继续压缩。", "若该点明显劣于 r146 且未优于 0.42x-0.55x 现有锚点，则可基本判定 shared-lowrank hetero residual 在线上价值不足，后续应停掉这条 family 的局部扫参。", "若结果介于 r146 与 <0.5x frontier 之间但仍形成新的中成本非支配段，可把它作为 0.5x-0.7x 结构锚点，再只改一个压缩旋钮验证是否能形成稳定 Pareto 段。"], "best_fvu": 0.09455648809671402, "last_round": 147}
