research/history/logs/agent_round_0198.stdout.log:1031:research/history/logs/agent_round_0191.stdout.log:3214:research/history/round_summaries/round_0184.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u5019\u9009 family \u8bbe\u4e3a `factorized_expert_topk`\u3002\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a `x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(h(x))} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}`\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0c`E(h(x))` \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0c`{b_{e,i}}` \u662f\u5404 expert \u7684\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\uff1b\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201cshared low-rank projection + \u8f7b\u91cf expert \u8def\u7531 + expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a `\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9`\u3002`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u8fd9\u7c7b batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u662f `\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9`\uff0c\u53ea\u80fd\u4f5c\u5386\u53f2\u53c2\u8003\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8\u5f53\u524d frontier\u3002r183 \u7684\u65b0 family `shared_two_stage_residual_expert` \u5728\u7ea6 `0.24x` \u4e0b\u4ec5\u505a\u5230 `FVU=0.1411`\uff0c\u8bf4\u660e\u201cshared coarse trunk + routed residual cleanup\u201d\u8fd9\u6761 two-stage \u53d8\u4f53\u6ca1\u6709\u6253\u8d25\u73b0\u6709 low-cost anchor\uff1b\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0b\u4e00\u6b65\u66f4\u9ad8\u4fe1\u606f\u91cf\u7684\u95ee\u9898\u4e0d\u662f\u7ee7\u7eed\u5728 shared/coarse \u7ebf\u4e0a\u8865\u53c2\u6570\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u8f6c\u5411\u5f53\u524d\u9ad8\u4f18\u5148\u7ea7\u4f46\u5c1a\u672a\u5728\u8fd9\u6761 exact low-cost recipe \u4e0a fresh \u9a8c\u8bc1\u7684\u201cexpert \u5185\u90e8 low-rank / small head\u201d\u69fd\u4f4d\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r176 \u53ea\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301 `K=108`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=64`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160`\u3001`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`\u3001`adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0e\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\uff0c\u76f4\u63a5\u56de\u7b54\u201c\u628a routed-only expert \u7684 full-dim \u5c40\u90e8 scorer \u6362\u6210 shared bottleneck + expert-specific small head\uff0c\u80fd\u5426\u5728\u66f4\u4f4e\u603b\u6210\u672c\u4e0b\u4fee\u590d r176 \u7684\u8d28\u91cf\u7f3a\u53e3\u201d\u3002\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\u663e\u793a\u8be5\u5019\u9009\u5728\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u4e0b selection_accesses=360448\u3001deployment_accesses=442368\u3001combined_accesses=802816\uff0c\u5bf9\u5e94 combined_ratio \u7ea6 `0.19x`\uff0c\u660e\u786e\u843d\u5728\u5f53\u524d `<0.25x` \u4e3b\u6218\u573a\u5185\uff0c\u4e5f\u663e\u8457\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0198.stdout.log:1090:research/history/logs/agent_round_0153.stdout.log:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式仍为 x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态全局 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“trunk 查表/加权和 + expert 子库 local top-k + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，所有库都为静态向量库、不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不得进入 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r152 仅把 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 从 2 降到 1，保持 `K=96`、`TRUNK_RANK=16`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 与其余训练配方不变，直接测试“全局 residual cleanup 是否足以支撑单 expert 激活路径”，从而把当前低成本最佳点从约 0.49x 进一步压到约 0.44x total_cost，同时尽量维持优于现有低成本前沿的 FVU。","summary":"建议以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1`。这不是继续细扫 `K` 轴，而是对当前最强低成本结构做一次更有结构信息的 matched-cost probe：验证 residual 补偿是否能让 `lowrank_expert_residual` 承受单 expert 路径，把总成本从约 0.49x 压到约 0.44x。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"这轮满足单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。之所以不继续顺着 `K` 做第三轮局部下压，是因为提示已明确要求不要让现有 family 的 K 轴邻域重新主导；`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 比 `K=88` 更能回答一个新的结构问题：当前 lowrank+expert+residual 是否仍需要双 expert 才能工作。之所以值得做，是因为本轮不是把 `expert_topk` 上对单 expert 的负信号简单外推到这里，相反是利用 residual cleanup 做一次 matched-cost 复验；本地成本自检显示 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 会把总成本从 2064384 压到 1835008，约 0.49x→0.44x，信息增量明显大于继续小步压 K。主要风险是 quality 可能明显回退；若如此，也能更干净地确认当前 target 上这条 family 的低成本下限确实依赖双 expert 路由。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"1"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r152 已把 `lowrank_expert_residual` 推到 `<0.5x`：`K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 时 FVU=0.09837，当前低成本前沿最佳点已从 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 切换到该 family。","本地成本自检：在 r152 配方下改成 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 后，deployment_accesses=458752 不变、combined_accesses=1835008、combined_ratio≈0.44，明显左于 r152 的 2064384/0.49x，且低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是在已有有效结构上验证“单 expert + residual 是否可行”，不是把 `expert_topk` 的单 expert 负信号直接外推；它更接近当前提示要求的 matched-cost 结构性对照。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 仍能保持 FVU 接近或优于当前 `<0.5x` best=0.0984，则下一轮可继续只改 `K` 或 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，把这条单 expert 路径进一步压向 0.4x 左右。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1` 明显失败，则可以更明确地记下：当前 target 上 `lowrank_expert_residual` 的低成本可用区仍依赖双 expert 路由，后续不应再在这条 family 上重复单 expert 试探。","如果该点形成新的非支配点但质量略退，则可把它作为更低成本 anchor，后续再决定是沿单 expert 分支继续压缩，还是回到新的 hetero-MoE family 做原型。"],"reference_round":152}
