ue":"two_stage_residual_expert"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r117 (`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3`) 与 r118 (`K=80`) 都未形成 shared_routed_expert_topk 的新非支配点，说明当前 `K=64-80, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=192` 子线已接近局部饱和；下一步应换 family，不应继续扫同一结构子线。","`two_stage_residual_expert` 已在当前工作区稳定注册并可直接实例化；本地 cost 估算显示在 `K=96, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=32, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 下 selection_accesses=2129920、deployment_accesses=393216、combined_accesses=2523136，combined_ratio 约 0.60，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束并落在允许的 0.3x-0.8x 结构性 anchor 带。","旧轮次只给弱先验：r53 在更高成本的 `K=192, NUM_EXPERTS=16` 下曾得到 FVU 0.1134，说明 `two_stage_residual_expert` 至少不是结构上明显失效的 family；但在当前 `K=96` recipe 上仍需 fresh validation，不能直接继承旧结论。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `two_stage_residual_expert K=96` 在约 0.60x 下把 FVU 压到接近 0.11-0.12，则下一轮应保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，验证 coarse 段与 expert residual 段的预算分配是否是主控制旋钮。","如果该 family 明显弱于 r98 的 `lowrank_expert_residual`，则说明在当前 target 上去掉 trunk 的代价过大；后续应停止把 `two-stage residual expert` 作为主线，并回到 `lowrank + expert (+ residual)` 方向继续压 encoder 成本。","如果该 family 质量介于 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 与 `lowrank_expert_residual` 之间且成本确实更低于 r98，则它仍可能形成新的中成本 Pareto 点；下一轮应优先沿 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO` 做单变量补点，而不是再开新 family。"],"reference_round":98}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0163.stdout.log:2042:research/history/logs/agent_round_0129.stdout.log:6828:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。","如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。","如果训练前或 sanity 阶段出现新问题，先按新 family registration/forward 问题处理，不要把失败误判为结构质量结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","fresh cost 自检：selection_accesses=1015808、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=1540096，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.37，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":128,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
