research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3604:research/history/logs/agent_round_0171.stdout.log:4081:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"160"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"候选 family 仍为 `lowrank_expert_topk`。最终重构公式保持为 `x_hat = Σ_r β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}`：其中 `{u_r}` 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，`{b_{e,i}}` 是静态 expert 子库原子；在线侧只需要计算 trunk 系数 `β_r(x)`、轻量 router 选出少量 expert，再在被选中的静态子库内做有限加权和。因此它可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表/加权和 + routed 子库查表 + 选择性补偿”流水线，兼容性判断为 `扩展兼容`；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 这类 batch/sample-coupled family 仍属不兼容，不能驱动当前 frontier。r170 已在 `<0.25x` 主战场上给出一个有价值信号：`lowrank_expert_topk` 在约 `0.24x` total_cost 下做到 `FVU=0.1404`，虽然尚未击败 `shared_routed_expert_topk K=112` 的 `0.1369`，但已明显接近，说明这条“轻 trunk + routed expert、无 residual cleanup”路线并未被证伪。当前最值得回答的单一问题不是继续回到 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 做更低信息量的局部细扫，而是：`lowrank_expert_topk` 能否在更低成本下仍维持对 low-cost anchors 的竞争力。故本轮以 r170 为 reference，只把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 压到 `160`，其余 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk, K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64, EXPANSION_FACTOR=1, adam, LR=8e-4` 保持不变，直接测试更小 per-expert width 是否能把该 family 从约 `0.24x` 压到约 `0.21x`，并在相近或更低成本下挑战当前 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 `0.20x-0.22x` 前沿段。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=160` 仍把 FVU 压在约 `0.145` 以内，则下一轮继续留在 `lowrank_expert_topk`，只改 `K`，定位它在 `0.20x-0.22x` 带内的 deployment knee。","如果该压缩后 FVU 明显退化到被同成本 `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors 支配，则可下调 `lowrank_expert_topk` 在当前 target 的优先级，回到别的轻量兼容 family，而不是继续沿这条线细扫。"],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_topk` 的 LUTurbo 导出形式是静态 trunk 库加少量 routed 静态 expert 子库上的有限加权和，兼容性应维持为扩展兼容。","本地 cost 自检显示：相对 r170，把 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 降到 `160` 后，`lowrank_expert_topk(K=96, TRUNK_RANK=16, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, NUM_EXPERTS=64)` 的 combined_accesses 约从 `1015808` 降到 `884736`，combined_ratio 约从 `0.24x` 降到 `0.21x`，仍稳居 `<0.25x` 主战场。","r166-r169 已基本说明继续在 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 上做同类小步细扫的信息增量有限；当前更高价值的是验证谁能在更低成本下逼近或击败它。"],"reference_round":170,"self_review":"这轮严格遵守单变量原则：以有效已跑通的 r170 为 reference，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`。选择这条轴而不是 `TRUNK_RANK`，是因为它带来的 total_cost 下压更明显，能更直接回答 `lowrank_expert_topk` 是否真能在更低成本段形成新前沿；主要风险是 expert width 压缩过头后质量退化，但这正是本轮需要澄清的核心问题。","summary":"以 r170 为 reference，仅将 `lowrank_expert_topk` 的 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 从 `224` 降到 `160`，测试这条扩展兼容的轻 trunk+routed-expert 路线能否把 total_cost 从约 `0.24x` 压到约 `0.21x`，同时仍保持对当前 low-cost `shared_routed_expert_topk` anchors 的竞争力。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3605:research/history/logs/agent_round_0138.stdout.log:1785:research/history/logs/agent_action_0129.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。","如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。","如果训练前或 sanity 阶段出现新问题，先按新 family registration/forward 问题处理，不要把失败误判为结构质量结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","fresh cost 自检：selection_accesses=1015808、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=1540096，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.37，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":128,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
