research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3685:research/history/logs/agent_round_0156.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下明显优于 r155 且接近当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，定位 coarse stage 与 residual expert 的分工边界。","如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则可把 shared-lowrank 两段式方向在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，下一轮转向更中成本但更有希望形成新段的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` matched probe。","如果该点仅小幅优于 r155 但仍不进入非支配前沿，则记录为 shared-lowrank coarse 比 shared-lowrank routed 更稳，但仍不足以替代现有 low-cost anchors，后续不要继续在该 family 上做连续局部微调。"],"notes_to_memory":["r155 已落盘：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 实际 FVU=0.14630839228630066，显著落后当前 0.28x-0.30x 低成本 frontier，因此不应继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。","当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=794624，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=1187840，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.28，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是对另一条高优先级结构槽位 `two-stage residual expert` 的 matched-cost 重验，不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或已失败的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续沿 r155 的 family 压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，是因为该 family 已在 128/112/96 三个成本配方上持续给出一致负信号；当前更高信息量的动作是切到尚未在现行 `K=96` 低成本 recipe 下复验的 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。本轮没有返回代码改动，因为该 family 已经落盘且本地 smoke 通过；主要风险是它在 r144 的 K=112 recipe 下也表现偏弱，但正因为 r155 已证明 routed top-k 线不足，当前最需要回答的是两段式 residual cleanup 是否比 routed-topk 更适合这个低成本带。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次面向 0.28x 低成本带的 matched architecture probe，用来回答 shared-lowrank 两段式 residual expert 是否比刚失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3686:research/history/logs/agent_round_0156.stdout.log:337:      "\u672c\u5730\u6210\u672c\u81ea\u68c0\uff1aselection_accesses=794624\uff0cdeployment_accesses=393216\uff0ccombined_accesses=1187840\uff0c\u5bf9\u5f53\u524d 1024x4096 proxy \u7684 combined_ratio\u22480.28\uff0c\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3687:research/history/logs/agent_round_0156.stdout.log:466:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"lower_cost","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + 轻量 router 选少量 experts + shared lookup + expert-local top-k lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答当前最高优先级的 hetero-MoE 结构“shared low-rank basis + expert-specific local head / local top-k”在约 0.28x total_cost 下，是否能优于现有 0.28x-0.32x 低成本 frontier 段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下接近或优于当前 0.28x-0.32x anchors，下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=192`，测试 shared scorer 还能否继续左移而不明显掉质。","如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则不要继续在 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 上做局部扫参，下一轮切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert` 做同 recipe 的 matched architecture probe。","如果结果异常差且与历史 r141 同向，可把“shared low-rank basis + routed local head”在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，转回别的未充分验证结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 inst��低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。","如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。","如果训练前或 sanity 阶段出现新问题，先按新 family registration/forward 问题处理，不要把失败误判为结构质量结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","fresh cost 自检：selection_accesses=1015808、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=1540096，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.37，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":128,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
