research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:3746:research/history/logs/agent_action_0150.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(h(x))} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j} + Σ_{m∈S_res(x-x_stage1)} γ_m(x) c_m，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是共享低秩投影，{b_i^sh} 是 shared 静态库，{b_{e,j}} 是 routed expert 静态子库，{c_m} 是全局 residual 静态补偿库，x_stage1 是 shared+routed factorized stage 的重构。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 推理链路时仍是“shared library lookup + routed expert sublibrary lookup + residual lookup + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：在保持 r146 的 matched recipe（K=112、EF=1、FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256、NUM_EXPERTS=64、ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2、LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224、STAGE1_RATIO=0.25 与其余训练配方不变）的前提下，新加 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 能回答当前最缺的结构问题：把 hetero MoE 的 shared+routed factorized head 再接上 residual cleanup，是否能在约 0.47x total_cost 下形成比现有 `<0.5x` anchor 更有价值的新结构段。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["若该点在约 0.47x 下优于当前 `<0.5x` 最佳 FVU=0.1010，则下一轮只改 `K` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO`，把这条新 hetero-MoE+residual 线继续向左压缩。","若该点接近但未优于 r146，则说明 factorized shared+routed stage 确有结构价值但不足以取代 trunk；后续可只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 验证瓶颈是否在 shared basis 宽度。","若该点明显劣于 r146 且不优于 r147/r148，则可更明确地终止当前 target 上“shared+routed factorized + residual”这条方向，避免继续在 hetero factorized family 上耗费预算。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`，真实修改文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`。","本地 allowlist 校验通过：`validate_env_overrides` 现在接受 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 搭配 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM`、`NUM_EXPERTS`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`、`STAGE1_RATIO`。","按架构接线 checklist 做了 exact smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual, K=112, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=1499136、deployment_accesses=458752、combined_accesses=1957888，对 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.47，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也左于 r146 matched recipe 的约 0.54x。","最近三条 fresh 结构对照结果分别是 r147 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` FVU=0.1038、r148 `two_stage_residual_expert` FVU=0.1140、r149 `factorized_expert_topk` FVU=0.2450；因此继续在这些已有 family 上做局部扫参的信息增量很低，本轮更适合补最小新原型。"],"reference_round":146,"self_review":"这轮选择 `edit_sae_code` 而不是再做现有 family 的 param-only probe，原因是当前已连续三轮 fresh 结构对照都未形成新非支配点，而提示明确要求在这种情况下优先切换到新的结构假设或新增最小可运行原型。新 family 不是无约束扩张：它直接填补了当前最缺的“shared experts + routed experts + expert-internal low-rank + residual cleanup”槽位，并且只复用现有 tunable 参数，没有新增 env key。风险在于 residual_encoder 仍然较重，可能重复 r147 的结论；但这次 factorized stage 把 stage1 selection 从约 0.44x 压到约 0.36x，足以提供新的结构信息。","summary":"已新增并接线 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual`，建议以 r146 为 reference，仅设置 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_routed_factorized_expert_residual` 启动首轮真实训练。它是一个已落盘、已 smoke、已过 allowlist 的最小新 family，目标是在当前最需要补证据的 0.3x-0.5x 带直接回答“hetero MoE 的 factorized shared+routed stage 加 residual cleanup”是否值得继续。","touched_files":["research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
