research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:4150:research/history/logs/agent_round_0157.stdout.log:496:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x-t(x))} γ_{e,j}(x) c_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx)，t(x)=Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) u_i，U={u_i} 是静态 shared 向量库，{C_e} 是静态 expert residual 子库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 时仍是“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + residual 上的 expert-local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此该 family 判定为扩展兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 等不兼容 family 仍不能驱动 frontier。本轮唯一主假设是：r155 已经把 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 明确证伪为当前 0.28x 低成本带的有效前沿候选，因此下一步不应继续在同一 family 上做局部扫参，而应切到另一条仍符合当前 agenda 的新结构槽位。相对当前低成本参考 r152，只把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `lowrank_expert_residual` 切到 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，保持 `K=96`、`EF=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 与其余训练 recipe 不变，直接回答“shared low-rank coarse stage + expert residual cleanup”在约 0.28x total_cost 下是否比已失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更接近当前低成本 frontier。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.28x 下明显优于 r155 且接近当前 0.28x-0.30x frontier，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，定位 coarse stage 与 residual expert 的分工边界。","如果该点仍明显落后于同成本 frontier，则可把 shared-lowrank 两段式方向在当前 target 的低成本主线优先级下调，下一轮转向更中成本但更有希望形成新段的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` matched probe。","如果该点仅小幅优于 r155 但仍不进入非支配前沿，则记录为 shared-lowrank coarse 比 shared-lowrank routed 更稳，但仍不足以替代现有 low-cost anchors，后续不要继续在该 family 上做连续局部微调。"],"notes_to_memory":["r155 已落盘：`shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk @ K=96` 实际 FVU=0.14630839228630066，显著落后当前 0.28x-0.30x 低成本 frontier，因此不应继续在该 family 上做局部扫参。","当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=794624，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=1187840，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.28，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮是对另一条高优先级结构槽位 `two-stage residual expert` 的 matched-cost 重验，不是继续打磨 `lowrank_expert_*` 或已失败的 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。之所以不继续沿 r155 的 family 压 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`，是因为该 family 已在 128/112/96 三个成本配方上持续给出一致负信号；当前更高信息量的动作是切到尚未在现行 `K=96` 低成本 recipe 下复验的 `shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。本轮没有返回代码改动，因为该 family 已经落盘且本地 smoke 通过；主要风险是它在 r144 的 K=112 recipe 下也表现偏弱，但正因为 r155 已证明 routed top-k 线不足，当前最需要回答的是两段式 residual cleanup 是否比 routed-topk 更适合这个低成本带。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_two_stage_residual_expert`。这是一次面向 0.28x 低成本带的 matched architecture probe，用来回答 shared-lowrank 两段式 residual expert 是否比刚失败的 shared-lowrank routed top-k 更值得继续。","touched_files":[]}
