x frontier。","当前代码已支持 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`，本轮不需要新增 tunable，也不需要修改 `research/AutoResearch/` 或 `scripts/`。","已用本轮精确 recipe 做本地 instantiate/forward/backward smoke：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual, K=96, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=224, STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 可正常运行。","本地成本自检：selection_accesses=1843200，deployment_accesses=393216，combined_accesses=2236416，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.53，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","这轮允许把预算上移到略高于 0.5x 的质量锚点，因为当前低成本两条 shared-lowrank 探针已连续失败；当前更重要的是回答 residual cleanup 是否能挽回这条 hetero-MoE 结构线。"],"reference_round":152,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量原则：相对 r152 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。我没有返回代码改动，因为该 family 已经落盘且本地 smoke 通过；本轮更重要的是利用当前 matched recipe 做一次干净的结构切换。之所以不继续沿 r155/r156 的 0.28x 线做 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` 或 `STAGE1_RATIO` 微调，是因为它们已经在当前 target 上给出几乎相同的失败结果；而 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual` 是当前 shared-lowrank 方向里唯一还有历史正信号、且仍符合 operator hint 的 hetero-MoE+residual 候选。主要风险是 K 从 112/128 压到 96 后，该 family 可能仍被 r152 直接压制；但即使失败，也能更干净地终止一条当前仍未完全回答的结构假设。","summary":"建议本轮以 r152 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_residual`。这是一次针对 hetero-MoE+residual 的 matched architecture probe，用来判断 shared-lowrank 方向在加入 residual cleanup 后，是否还能形成一个值得保留的 0.5x 左右结构锚点。","touched_files":[]}
research/history/logs/agent_round_0175.stdout.log:4153:research/history/logs/agent_round_0129.stdout.log:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_sh(h(x))} α_i^sh(x) u_i + Σ_{e∈E(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=Bx 是共享低秩投影，U={u_i} 是静态 shared library，{B_e} 是静态 routed expert 子库。在线侧可导出为“shared low-rank projection + shared library lookup + routed expert local top-k + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk` 判定为直接兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 仍是不兼容 family，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设：相对 r128 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `shared_routed_factorized_expert_topk` 切到已实际落盘的新 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，保持 `K=128`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 与其余训练配方不变，直接回答 r127-r128 的负信号是否主要来自“routed experts 也被一并 factorize”这一结构限制；如果是，则新 family 应在 fresh cost 约 selection=0.24x、deployment=0.12x、total=0.37x 的低成本带显著优于 0.2248，并决定这条 shared-lowrank + full-routed-head 结构是否值得继续扩展。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该点在约 0.37x 下把 FVU 明显拉回到接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 低成本前沿，则下一轮保持新 family 不变，只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=384` 或 `K=112`，定位这条新线的 low-cost knee。","如果结果只小幅优于 r128 但仍明显差于现有 `<0.5x` frontier，则可初步判定问题不只在 routed factorization，本方向优先级应下调，后续转回 `two_stage_residual_expert` 或别的未充分验证结构。","如果训练前或 sanity 阶段出现新问题，先按新 family registration/forward 问题处理，不要把失败误判为结构质量结论。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际新增并注册 `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，真实改动仅落在 `sparsify/config.py` 与 `sparsify/sparse_coder.py`。","本地 exact architecture smoke 已通过：`ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk, K=128, EF=1, FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256, NUM_EXPERTS=64, ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=320` 可 instantiate/forward/backward。","fresh cost 自检：selection_accesses=1015808、deployment_accesses=524288、combined_accesses=1540096，对当前 1024x4096 proxy 的 combined_ratio≈0.37，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。"],"reference_round":128,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：计划运行时相对 r128 只改 `ARCHITECTURE`。这轮不是回到旧 family 的局部扫参，而是落一个最小新原型，直接隔离“shared+routed 失败是否来自把 routed heads 也 factorize”这个高信息量结构问题。按 `sae-architecture-integration` 检查，whitelist、factory dispatch、具体类实现和 exact architecture smoke 都已完成；主要风险是 routed full heads 会把行为拉回接近 `shared_routed_expert_topk` 而缺乏新的 Pareto 价值，但这本身也是清晰结论。","summary":"已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`：shared 分支保留低秩 scorer，routed experts 改回 full-dim local heads，用来做对 r127-r128 的最小结构修正。建议本轮以 r128 为 reference，只改 `ARCHITECTURE=shared_lowrank_routed_expert_topk`，用同配方直接判断当前 shared+routed 负信号是否主要来自过度 factorize routed experts。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py"]}
